JOHANNESBURG - Kaizer Chiefs will on Thursday be revealing their new home and away kit for the 2017/18 season.According to the Amakhosi, the kit design is a fusion of the club s rich heritage and modern style indicative of the future potential of the powerful squad.The kit features high-performance materials and lightweight construction in traditional club colours, crafted to enhance ventilation and moisture management, and increase the athletes ease of motion and precision.The first team will debut the home kit in their Carling Black Label Champion Cup match against Orlando Pirates at the FNB Stadium on Saturday, 29 July. eNCA